                     <interp inst="t18240218-119-person1178" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am constable. He was brought to the watch-house. I asked how he did it; he said he reached over the counter and took it.</p>
               <p>GUILTY. Aged 14.</p>
